{"tid":1247304,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【傘運2.0】正苦冷處理，群眾失方向，自亂陣腳","createTime":"2019-06-21T05:06:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-21T05:59:02.000Z","uid":264624,"like":15,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"219e8d246637bc6d00867897dafd16fec3dc7a11","tid":1247304,"uid":264624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T05:06:33.000Z","msg":"當年發夢仲有熱普城攪分化，最終失敗！<br />\n<br />\n而家聞到味，好似有蹟象重蹈覆轍，個個見到冇哂狗就冇咗目標，加埋大量分化撚滲入人群放假消息，市民開始唔知要跟邊個做，訊息開始混亂，又有傳紙仔出現去擾亂冇tg冇上連登嘅人，同5年前個夢好似，我哋<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>俾人拆緊「大台」！</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n子華神講過「曆史從來都係冇教育意義」,我好明白好多人都好心急想「做啲嘢」, 但都要時刻警覺保持清醒，要用智慧去拆解敵人既軟攻勢，要得分唔一定要自己主動出擊，可以等對家擺烏龍失分！真係好驚呢次又行返雨傘條路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97d9c8ea37e774789efa1845f215fa1538464281","tid":1247304,"uid":264624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T05:07:18.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea928abdb9082c2184dbb5ac47f327fcb182757c","tid":1247304,"uid":264624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T05:08:33.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65fadd16e88ad4262d69c7addaca7813b93aaa6a","tid":1247304,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T05:09:57.000Z","msg":"香港發生咁多事會唔會多咗人報案？"},{"pid":"9efc1a5ad3f39da052c75d527735c89780f89dbd","tid":1247304,"uid":264624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T05:10:26.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2b8468dc216b554b05ef4201be2457037ca6c38","tid":1247304,"uid":264624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T05:11:34.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7f1078aa6fcf08551239df9c30a6bb535e8b319","tid":1247304,"uid":264624,"like":0,"d